31:12.037 --> 31:14.446
♪<i> I love to feel the rain</i> ♪

31:14.598 --> 31:18.166
♪<i> On my face,</i>
<i> taste the rain on my lips</i> ♪

31:19.044 --> 31:21.628
♪<i> In the moonlight shadow</i> ♪

31:23.716 --> 31:25.716
