31:25.943 --> 31:27.609
♪<i> Heart of mine</i> ♪

31:27.628 --> 31:30.295
♪<i> It puts a smile</i>
<i> on my face every time</i> ♪

31:30.447 --> 31:34.207
♪<i> 'Cause I love a rainy night</i> ♪

31:34.226 --> 31:37.728
♪<i> Yeah, I love a rainy night</i> ♪

31:37.897 --> 31:41.047
♪<i> Well, I love a rainy night</i> ♪

31:41.066 --> 31:42.733
♪<i> Well, I love a rainy night</i> ♪

31:42.884 --> 31:44.384
♪<i> Ooh, ooh</i> ♪

31:44.478 --> 31:46.361
♪<i> Take it away, y'all...</i> ♪

31:51.059 --> 31:52.576
Come on.

31:52.803 --> 31:55.895
♪<i> Showers wash</i>
<i> all of my cares away</i> ♪

31:55.973 --> 31:59.975
