32:33.118 --> 32:35.994
-♪<i> Yeah, yeah, yeah.</i> ♪
-(Nicky whoops)

32:41.126 --> 32:43.293
(soft music playing)

32:43.520 --> 32:44.352
Try some.

32:44.371 --> 32:45.704
Well, I know you
weren't thrilled

32:45.856 --> 32:46.964
to be singing tonight, but you

32:47.191 --> 32:48.873
got to admit, we make some
pretty beautiful music

32:48.968 --> 32:51.376
-together.
-Yeah, onstage.

32:51.528 --> 32:57.032
Onstage and offstage, and
in elevators and hotel suites.

32:57.050 --> 32:59.309
(laughs softly)
Can I buy you a drink?

33:00.312 --> 33:02.387
I think you'll find
they're free.

33:02.539 --> 33:04.231
Of course.

33:06.101 --> 33:07.359
Excuse me.

33:08.395 --> 33:10.070
Hey.

33:10.972 --> 33:13.139
The show must go on. Is that it?

33:13.158 --> 33:15.884
Yeah, sometimes I have
obligations that go

33:15.886 --> 33:17.661
beyond what's happening
right now.

33:17.812 --> 33:20.163
You mean, beyond Dad?

33:21.500 --> 33:22.891
Please don't be angry.

33:22.984 --> 33:24.835
I'm done being angry.

33:25.062 --> 33:27.045
It doesn't change anything.

33:31.159 --> 33:33.068
(indistinct chatter)

33:33.086 --> 33:35.161
-Oh, no.
-What?

33:35.255 --> 33:38.073
We lost the cover.

33:38.166 --> 33:39.999
"In light of recent
developments..."

33:40.093 --> 33:42.686
meaning they saw your post and
realize how shallow they are,

33:42.913 --> 33:46.189
"...we've decided to go in
a different creative direction."

33:46.341 --> 33:48.525
-I'm sorry, Geeg.
-Hey.

33:48.752 --> 33:51.028
If they didn't want the real me,
it's their loss.

33:51.221 --> 33:53.438
I know who I am.

33:53.532 --> 33:55.532
And I'm done pretending
to be anybody else.

33:55.759 --> 33:57.159
Cheers to that.

33:59.596 --> 34:01.429
Hey. Thank you.

34:01.448 --> 34:03.598
We just secured
worldwide distribution.

34:03.617 --> 34:06.209
In no small part thanks to you
blowing the roof off the place.

34:06.361 --> 34:08.953
I mean it, Nick.
You killed it tonight.

34:09.048 --> 34:10.964
I'm sensing a "but."

34:12.776 --> 34:15.960
-Mackenzie Gates didn't show.
-Okay, so all that pretending,

34:16.055 --> 34:19.114
as you put, um,
that was for nothing.

34:19.132 --> 34:20.298
No, it wasn't for nothing.

34:20.450 --> 34:21.558
Oh, yeah, 'cause
I'm forgetting about

34:21.709 --> 34:23.451
the silver lining
that now my daughter hates me.

34:23.470 --> 34:25.545
We just have to show
Open Horizon

34:25.564 --> 34:28.306
what every other person
here saw tonight, okay?

34:28.458 --> 34:30.067
That you deserve a tour.

34:30.218 --> 34:32.235
I'm gonna get you one.

34:32.462 --> 34:33.737
I promise.

34:36.800 --> 34:38.075
Hey.

34:38.302 --> 34:39.467
How you doing, kiddo?

34:39.561 --> 34:41.912
I don't know how everyone
is just celebrating

34:42.063 --> 34:44.247
like nothing's going on.

34:45.250 --> 34:46.899
What if my dad needs help?

34:46.919 --> 34:49.669
The police are doing
everything they can.

34:51.090 --> 34:53.665
Now, can I be honest with you?

34:53.759 --> 34:57.052
I think you're old enough
to hear this straight.

34:59.747 --> 35:04.326
I think your dad needed a break,
and he just took one.

35:04.419 --> 35:07.086
Sorry, but he wouldn't do that.

35:07.164 --> 35:09.347
And I'm sick of every time
that I bring it up,

35:09.441 --> 35:11.090
everyone seems like
there's something

35:11.110 --> 35:13.193
that they just,
they can't tell me.

35:14.929 --> 35:16.947
Excuse me.

35:17.098 --> 35:20.008
Hey, little girl.

35:20.026 --> 35:23.862
-(exhales)
-What was that about?

35:24.014 --> 35:26.181
That was about
Nicky's little girl

35:26.199 --> 35:28.850
really missing her daddy.

35:28.869 --> 35:31.795
Yeah, well, we all do.

35:31.964 --> 35:35.448
-I hope we hear from him soon.
-Mm-hmm.

35:35.467 --> 35:39.136
Albie, if there was
something I needed to know,

35:39.287 --> 35:41.138
you'd tell me, right?

35:42.123 --> 35:43.789
You'd be my first call.

35:43.884 --> 35:45.392
All right.

35:55.654 --> 35:58.488
♪ ♪

36:06.665 --> 36:08.582
(sighs)

36:10.502 --> 36:12.169
(door closes)

36:14.064 --> 36:15.397
How's the leg?

36:15.415 --> 36:17.323
Well, it's got a hole in it.

36:18.585 --> 36:21.344
Of course, it's nothing
compared to the one in my heart.

36:21.496 --> 36:24.255
Aww. And they call<i> me</i>
the drama queen.

36:24.349 --> 36:26.908
(laughs softly)
You look beautiful.

36:26.927 --> 36:29.269
Save the sweet talk.

36:31.097 --> 36:33.206
Are you here to take me back?

36:33.208 --> 36:38.344
I'm gonna take you back,
on one condition:

36:38.438 --> 36:41.013
you're through
with this outlaw crap.

36:41.107 --> 36:44.275
It was cute when we were 20,
but I'm over it.

36:44.428 --> 36:46.519
What does that even mean?

36:46.538 --> 36:50.281
It means no more
trashing hotel rooms,

36:50.434 --> 36:52.242
it means no more
getting into fights.

36:52.394 --> 36:55.194
I am not gonna be
a prison widow again.

36:55.214 --> 36:58.531
And you know, your music's
got to grow up, too.

36:58.625 --> 37:00.291
I mean, you got to stop writing
these songs about getting drunk

37:00.385 --> 37:04.638
and start writing some deep,
meaningful crap.

37:05.782 --> 37:08.040
I know you have it in you.

37:08.118 --> 37:11.728
That's what the love
of a good woman will do.

37:11.879 --> 37:13.972
(exhales)
I don't understand, Dot.

37:14.124 --> 37:16.458
We are gonna rebrand you,
big guy.

37:16.476 --> 37:19.885
You are now
the Texas Truth-teller, huh?

37:19.905 --> 37:22.572
That's got a nice ring to it.

37:22.799 --> 37:25.575
Yeah, that ring
is total malarkey, darling.

37:25.727 --> 37:28.394
(chuckles)

37:28.488 --> 37:29.621
Okay.

37:30.657 --> 37:31.748
Deal.

37:35.829 --> 37:37.312
DOTTIE:
Deal.

37:37.330 --> 37:40.648
But what am I gonna tell
the press about the leg?

37:40.742 --> 37:43.260
Uh, simple, we're gonna
tell them the truth.

37:43.487 --> 37:48.490
That you got into a fight with
some drunks outside of my gig,

37:48.583 --> 37:53.270
you fought them off,
but then, one of them had a gun

37:53.497 --> 37:55.605
and he shot you.

37:55.832 --> 37:58.441
You are one piece of work.

37:58.668 --> 38:00.593
Thank you.

38:00.612 --> 38:04.614
I thought I lost you
for good this time.

38:08.194 --> 38:12.122
(whispering): No.
You're my Texas Truth-teller.

38:12.349 --> 38:14.958
<i> Nothing's gonna tear us apart.</i>

38:20.799 --> 38:22.040
-(phone chimes)
-"I knew she had

38:22.134 --> 38:23.282
"the voice of an angel,

38:23.302 --> 38:25.969
but she has
the heart of one, too."

38:26.120 --> 38:28.546
(laughs)

38:28.640 --> 38:30.198
What on earth?

38:30.216 --> 38:32.884
Oh, it's just one of thousands

38:32.960 --> 38:34.811
of comments posted
under your video.

38:34.962 --> 38:38.556
And #ScrewBeaucoupsMagazine
is trending.

38:38.633 --> 38:41.042
-You're kidding.
-No. You're an inspiration.

38:41.061 --> 38:43.227
Look, this little girl posted
a pic wearing your outfit.

38:44.323 --> 38:48.049
"Gigi Roman is as beautiful
as any supermodel."

38:48.142 --> 38:51.219
Oh, bless her little heart.

38:51.237 --> 38:55.390
They love you for being you.

38:55.408 --> 38:56.833
Just like I do.

38:57.002 --> 38:59.002
All I did is tell the truth.

38:59.153 --> 39:01.212
That's all I ever wanted to do.

39:04.401 --> 39:06.584
<i> NICKY:</i>
<i> You wanted to see me, Daddy?</i>

39:06.678 --> 39:08.094
Close the door.

39:11.332 --> 39:15.000
So they had this whole party
to celebrate

39:15.095 --> 39:17.687
the Texas Truth-teller.

39:17.839 --> 39:20.339
That's you, Daddy.

39:20.433 --> 39:22.341
No, it's not.

39:22.361 --> 39:25.528
There's been too many secrets
and too many lies

39:25.680 --> 39:28.198
floating around here
for too long.

39:28.349 --> 39:31.368
It's time we start
clearing them up.

39:32.371 --> 39:33.945
Right.

39:34.097 --> 39:36.264
You know I had an affair
a long time ago.

39:36.282 --> 39:37.957
Mm-hmm.

39:38.952 --> 39:41.193
Well, it turns out, the woman,

39:41.213 --> 39:45.548
Rosa... she had a child.

39:46.793 --> 39:48.134
Okay.

39:51.631 --> 39:53.431
Your mama found out about it.

39:56.228 --> 39:59.137
And she locked them in the barn
and she burned it down.

39:59.305 --> 40:00.730
She wouldn't do that.

40:00.882 --> 40:02.732
She did.

40:05.128 --> 40:07.404
But the baby survived.

40:09.074 --> 40:12.033
And that baby is Catt Phoenix.

40:13.803 --> 40:15.319
I don't believe it.

40:15.472 --> 40:18.206
I'm sorry, darling,
but it's true.

40:21.086 --> 40:23.661
Country's perfect family.

40:23.755 --> 40:25.296
(scoffs)

40:27.241 --> 40:30.576
Lies are the real Roman legacy.

40:30.628 --> 40:34.431
And your mama and I
passed them on to you.

40:37.160 --> 40:39.436
And now I'm gonna
pass them on to my children.

40:46.427 --> 40:49.854
♪<i> Somewhere in the distance</i> ♪

40:50.023 --> 40:53.024
♪<i> Fading with the sun</i> ♪

40:53.118 --> 40:56.027
♪<i> Can hear it if you listen</i> ♪

40:56.121 --> 40:59.789
♪<i> Darkness on the run...</i> ♪

40:59.958 --> 41:02.441
-Mom?
-Hey. (shushes)

41:02.461 --> 41:06.111
I'm sorry.
I didn't mean to wake you.

41:06.131 --> 41:09.299
I know you're going
through a hard time.

41:12.028 --> 41:13.528
I just want you
to know that I'll always

41:13.697 --> 41:16.181
be here for you, okay?

41:18.034 --> 41:20.185
I'll always be here.

41:21.204 --> 41:23.204
(knocking on door)

41:23.297 --> 41:24.647
You wanted to see me, sir?

41:24.799 --> 41:27.558
Yeah, how we doing
with that task force?

41:27.711 --> 41:28.985
The Clive Grayson case?

41:29.136 --> 41:30.135
I'm not doing anything.

41:30.155 --> 41:31.729
I thought you wanted
to keep it quiet.

41:31.881 --> 41:32.930
I mean,
given the celebrity angle

41:32.991 --> 41:34.899
and the fact
that your friends are...

41:35.051 --> 41:37.235
My friends deserve
to have the full resources

41:37.387 --> 41:40.330
of this office devoted
to finding that man.

41:40.481 --> 41:42.165
A little girl
is missing her father,

41:42.316 --> 41:44.650
and we owe it to them
to get to the truth,

41:44.744 --> 41:48.079
whatever it takes,
and whoever it hurts.

41:48.231 --> 41:50.915
-Are we in agreement, Detective?
-Yes, sir.

41:51.067 --> 41:52.992
I'll get right on it.

41:53.011 --> 41:55.178
